utoScroll is false, you can drive the slices and how they look on the screen.  You can send all the slices at once or send one at a time and animate it onto the screen at the current time.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ScrollLayout","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"ScrollLayout","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ScrollLayout"}],"type":"topic"}}}